{
  "stem": "13469.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This was part of the earlier registration process, of course.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they knew where we lived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they came around to our door and banged on the door and told us we had half an hour to come out into the nearby square.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] thinks that the SS actually missed us, and that they couldn't find us, and that there was a Nazi sympathizer on the other side of the street who pointed out to them that they'd missed us and they came back for us.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know whether it's true, but they came in any case.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I should, perhaps, say that in Holland, there was a Nazi party who collaborated with the Germans, with the Nazis, but it was a relatively small number of people called NSB.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the Dutch Nazi party.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they were severely dealt with after the war by the Dutch people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The vast majority of Dutch people were not on the side of the Nazis, but there were some.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were, of course, benefits of being on the Nazi side during the war, during the occupation.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I suppose they must have banged on the door.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't suppose I opened the door.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It would've been my father who would open the door.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they would tell us we had to come out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We could hear it on the loud speakers, and we could see all the commotion outside, with people walking up and down with all their luggage.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were already packed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, this was another law that I haven't mentioned because there's millions of laws.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a law where it said that all Jews had to be prepared to go to a camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
